{"tid":2435044,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"杜麗冰法官公布將於本月11日及13日聽取覆核聆訊","createTime":"2021-03-06T02:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:41:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"74165992da5ac3a176b7ef4a28d0fbd13134c3d2","tid":2435044,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14179&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=d2c66546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14179</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第七庭<br />\n#杜麗冰法官 #指定法官 <br />\n#提訊 #港區國安法 #初選47人 <br />\n<br />\nD8:鄭達鴻<br />\n法律代表：#潘熙資深大律師<br />\n<br />\n申請人： <br />\n副刑事檢控專員(特別職務) #楊美琪女士<br />\n<br />\n申請人向法庭索取指示，警方於日後聆訊為法庭使用者進行安檢<br />\n<br />\n法庭考慮了人身自由，認為應盡快進行聆訊，但雙方需充足時間準備，讓法庭全面考慮雙方理據。因此，法庭指示律政司需要於8/3午飯前呈交傳票，5pm前呈交誓章及書面陳詞。法庭指示答辯人需要於10/3 5pm前呈交書面陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n法庭指示11/3及13/3上午及下午進行保釋覆核聆訊，各時段處理3個保釋覆核申請，每個申請預計需時1小時。<br />\n<br />\n法庭指會就每一個申請分別頒發判案書<br />\n<br />\n申請人指倉卒時間下未能為所有證據提交中文譯本，杜麗冰法官笑指自己能閱讀中文"},{"pid":"9f0fdc3fd269a1377f86a55d8f31f5be2da9ead4","tid":2435044,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411f93e805bab5cba1cb863a6fb2e7cb876cfd97","tid":2435044,"uid":95577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"又拖幾日<br />\n應該俾暫時人保釋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fbfc831e550cf9a355b8cba3e32370d8480921","tid":2435044,"uid":36432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"未審先剝奪你人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DOJ